    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sets of wallpapers which consist of separate printed elements, including borders and plain or elaborate fill papers, used in combination to create the effect of panels on the wall.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
